resources.string:
Hi! I've discovered an app called "Login".
You will be able to seamlessly log into ISP Login page using this app.
Now only Wishnet is supported.
The app isn't now available in the store.
You can grab a copy of the latest package from Github.

https://github.com/ExploiTR/Login/releases

This application is only to be used for personal/non-commercial usage and must be used on networks for which you have permission to do so. Any other use will not be the responsibility of the developer.In other words, you will be responsible for what you do.
